  <summary>5/25/2001--Introduced.
Energy Efficient Appliances Act of 2001 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide an annual credit of 50 percent of the amount paid by a taxpayer for the purchase of a qualified energy efficient appliance (and proper disposal of the old appliance). Limits the credit to $1,000 per individual per year.</summary>
